<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Kentucky Mountain Bible College grants Advanced Placement credit for some subjects. Students who have completed an Advanced Placement Examination under the College Board should have their scores sent directly to the Registrar. Credit will not be given for institutional examinations of other colleges and universities. The record will indicate that the credit is for the Advanced Placement Examinations Program, and the specific examination for which credit is given will be listed with the hours of credit given.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://catalog.mykmbc.org/" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

